            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
            <section ID="La6a54077-60a2-484a-9570-d464e0aeb9bb">
               <id root="1d9acef4-6d95-47de-ae9a-3fed723953fd"/>
               <code code="34069-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title>SUPPLY</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Bimox® (amoxicillin) for oral suspension is supplied in bottles containing 0.75 g of amoxicillin activity in bottles of 15 mL or 1.5 g of amoxicillin<br/>activity in bottles of 30 mL. After reconstitution with the required amount of water, each mL will contain 50 mg of amoxicillin as the trihydrate.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20211220"/>
            </section>
         </component>
